and cs index). After \code{\link[=snap_to_ref]{snap_to_ref()}} also \code{x0sn}
/ \code{pcisn} (post-RefPA center and cs index, with \code{NA} for peaks
snapped beyond \code{maxCombine}). \code{A} and \code{lambda} are preserved
through every stage.
